xt and any','line_number':52,'multiline':False]['text':'   of its associated I/O objects (such as sockets and timers) occur in only','line_number':53,'multiline':False]['text':'   one thread at a time.','line_number':54,'multiline':False]['text':'','line_number':55,'multiline':False]['text':' - Asynchronous resolve operations fail with operation_not_supported.','line_number':56,'multiline':False]['text':'','line_number':57,'multiline':False]['text':' - If a signal_set is used with the io_context, signal_set objects cannot be','line_number':58,'multiline':False]['text':'   used with any other io_context in the program.','line_number':59,'multiline':False]['text':' This special concurrency hint disables locking in the reactor I/O. This hint','line_number':63,'multiline':False]['text':' has the following restrictions:','line_number':64,'multiline':False]['text':'','line_number':65,'multiline':False]['text':' - Care must be taken to ensure that run functions on the io_context, and all','line_number':66,'multiline':False]['text':'   operations on the io_context's associated I/O objects (such as sockets and','line_number':67,'multiline':False]['text':'   timers), occur in only one thread at a time.','line_number':68,'multiline':False]['text':' The special concurrency hint provides full thread safety.','line_number':74,'multiline':False]['text':' This #define may be overridden at compile time to specify a program-wide','line_number':81,'multiline':False]['text':' default concurrency hint, used by the zero-argument io_context constructor.','line_number':82,'multiline':False]['text':' !defined(ASIO_CONCURRENCY_HINT_DEFAULT)','line_number':85,'multiline':False]['text':' This #define may be overridden at compile time to specify a program-wide','line_number':87,'multiline':False]['text':' concurrency hint, used by the one-argument io_context constructor when','line_number':88,'multiline':False]['text':' passed a value of 1.','line_number':89,'multiline':False]['text':' !defined